            "Astral develops open source Python projects including uv, ruff, and ty.",
            "The acquisition aims to accelerate the growth of OpenAI's Codex.",
            "This move is intended to power the next generation of Python developer tools."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "Astral 开发了包括 uv、ruff 和 ty 在内的开源 Python 项目。",
            "此次收购旨在加速 OpenAI 的 Codex 项目发展。",
            "此举旨在为下一代 Python 开发者工具提供支持。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "The integration of Astral's Python infrastructure tools into OpenAI's operations could streamline development workflows and enhance the capabilities of AI models reliant on Python tooling.",
          "zh": "将 Astral 的 Python 基础设施工具整合到 OpenAI 的运营中，可能会简化开发工作流程，并增强依赖 Python 工具的 AI 模型的能力。"
        },
